    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Employee
    An abstract class representing an employee in the payroll system.
    FullTimeEmployee
    Represents a full-time employee and their salary details.
    Menu
    payrollsystem.Menu class to run and operate the command line interface and associated functions
    MenuSimulation
    MenuSimulation class for running the command-line payroll system.
    PartTimeEmployee
    Represents a part-time employee and their associated pay details.
    PayRollException
    A custom exception class for handling payroll related exceptions
    PayRollSystem
    Manages the back end of the payroll system, including employees, positions and payslips.
    Payslip
    Represents a payslip for an employee, including all earnings and deductions.
    Position
    Represents a position within the university payroll system Has a position title, a category, and a payscale
